{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.1","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:1","prev_osis_id":"Acts.028.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Adresse et salutation<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-7: cf. Tit 1:1-4. Ga 1:1-5.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Paul, serviteur de J\u00e9sus-Christ, appel\u00e9 \u00e0 \u00eatre ap\u00f4tre, mis \u00e0 part pour annoncer l\u2019\u00c9vangile de Dieu,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.2","name":"Romains 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.28.31","name":"Actes 28:31","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.28.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.2","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:2","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>qui avait \u00e9t\u00e9 promis auparavant de la part de Dieu par ses proph\u00e8tes dans les saintes \u00c9critures,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.3","name":"Romains 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.1","name":"Romains 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.3","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:3","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>et qui concerne son Fils (n\u00e9 de la post\u00e9rit\u00e9 de David, selon la chair,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.4","name":"Romains 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.2","name":"Romains 1:2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.4","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:4","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>et d\u00e9clar\u00e9 Fils de Dieu avec puissance, selon l\u2019Esprit de saintet\u00e9, par sa r\u00e9surrection d\u2019entre les morts), J\u00e9sus-Christ notre Seigneur,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.5","name":"Romains 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.3","name":"Romains 1:3","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.5","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:5","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>par qui nous avons re\u00e7u la gr\u00e2ce et l\u2019apostolat, pour amener en son nom \u00e0 l\u2019ob\u00e9issance de la foi tous les pa\u00efens,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.6","name":"Romains 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.4","name":"Romains 1:4","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.6","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:6","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>parmi lesquels vous \u00eates aussi, vous qui avez \u00e9t\u00e9 appel\u00e9s par J\u00e9sus-Christ,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.7","name":"Romains 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.5","name":"Romains 1:5","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.7","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:7","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>\u00e0 tous ceux qui, \u00e0 Rome, sont bien-aim\u00e9s de Dieu, appel\u00e9s \u00e0 \u00eatre saints: que la gr\u00e2ce et la paix vous soient donn\u00e9es de la part de Dieu notre P\u00e8re et du Seigneur J\u00e9sus-Christ!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.8","name":"Romains 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.6","name":"Romains 1:6","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.8","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:8","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.009,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Amour de Paul pour les chr\u00e9tiens de Rome. Son d\u00e9sir d\u2019aller les voir<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 8-15: cf. (1 Th 1:2, 3, 8; 3:7-13.) Ro 15:23-32.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Je rends d\u2019abord gr\u00e2ces \u00e0 mon Dieu par J\u00e9sus-Christ, au sujet de vous tous, de ce que votre foi est renomm\u00e9e dans le monde entier.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.9","name":"Romains 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.7","name":"Romains 1:7","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.9","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:9","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Dieu, que je sers en mon esprit dans l\u2019\u00c9vangile de son Fils, m\u2019est t\u00e9moin que je fais sans cesse mention de vous,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.10","name":"Romains 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.8","name":"Romains 1:8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.10","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:10","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>demandant continuellement dans mes pri\u00e8res d\u2019avoir enfin, par sa volont\u00e9, le bonheur d\u2019aller vers vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.11","name":"Romains 1:11","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.9","name":"Romains 1:9","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.11","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:11","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Car je d\u00e9sire vous voir, pour vous communiquer quelque don spirituel, afin que vous soyez affermis,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.12","name":"Romains 1:12","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.10","name":"Romains 1:10","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.12","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:12","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>ou plut\u00f4t, afin que nous soyons encourag\u00e9s ensemble au milieu de vous par la foi qui nous est commune, \u00e0 vous et \u00e0 moi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.13","name":"Romains 1:13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.11","name":"Romains 1:11","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.13","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:13","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Je ne veux pas vous laisser ignorer, fr\u00e8res, que j\u2019ai souvent form\u00e9 le projet d\u2019aller vous voir, afin de recueillir quelque fruit parmi vous, comme parmi les autres nations; mais j\u2019en ai \u00e9t\u00e9 emp\u00each\u00e9 jusqu\u2019ici.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.14","name":"Romains 1:14","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.12","name":"Romains 1:12","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.14","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:14","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Je me dois aux Grecs et aux barbares, aux savants et aux ignorants.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.15","name":"Romains 1:15","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.13","name":"Romains 1:13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.15","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:15","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Ainsi j\u2019ai un vif d\u00e9sir de vous annoncer aussi l\u2019\u00c9vangile, \u00e0 vous qui \u00eates \u00e0 Rome.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.16","name":"Romains 1:16","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.14","name":"Romains 1:14","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.16","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:16","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.017,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La justice par la foi, sujet de l\u2019\u00e9p\u00eetre<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 16-17: cf. Mc 16:15, 16. 1 Co 1:18-24. Ro 3:21-25.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>\n    Car je n\u2019ai point honte de l\u2019\u00c9vangile: c\u2019est une puissance de Dieu pour le salut de quiconque croit, du Juif premi\u00e8rement, puis du Grec,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.17","name":"Romains 1:17","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.15","name":"Romains 1:15","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.17","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:17","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>parce qu\u2019en lui est r\u00e9v\u00e9l\u00e9e la justice de Dieu par la foi et pour la foi, selon qu\u2019il est \u00e9crit: Le juste vivra par la foi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.18","name":"Romains 1:18","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.16","name":"Romains 1:16","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.18","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:18","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.019,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">\u00c9tat de p\u00e9ch\u00e9 et de condamnation de l\u2019humanit\u00e9<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 18-32: cf. (Ps 19:2-5. Ac 14:16, 17.) (Ps 81:12, 13. \u00c9s 44:9-20.) (\u00c9p 4:17-19. 1 Pi 4:3-5.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>La col\u00e8re de Dieu se r\u00e9v\u00e8le du ciel contre toute impi\u00e9t\u00e9 et toute injustice des hommes qui retiennent injustement la v\u00e9rit\u00e9 captive,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.19","name":"Romains 1:19","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.17","name":"Romains 1:17","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.19","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:19","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>car ce qu\u2019on peut conna\u00eetre de Dieu est manifeste pour eux, Dieu le leur ayant fait conna\u00eetre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.20","name":"Romains 1:20","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.18","name":"Romains 1:18","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.20","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:20","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>En effet, les perfections invisibles de Dieu, sa puissance \u00e9ternelle et sa divinit\u00e9, se voient comme \u00e0 l\u2019\u0153il, depuis la cr\u00e9ation du monde, quand on les consid\u00e8re dans ses ouvrages. Ils sont donc inexcusables,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.21","name":"Romains 1:21","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.19","name":"Romains 1:19","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.21","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:21","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>puisque ayant connu Dieu, ils ne l\u2019ont point glorifi\u00e9 comme Dieu, et ne lui ont point rendu gr\u00e2ces; mais ils se sont \u00e9gar\u00e9s dans leurs pens\u00e9es, et leur c\u0153ur sans intelligence a \u00e9t\u00e9 plong\u00e9 dans les t\u00e9n\u00e8bres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.22","name":"Romains 1:22","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.20","name":"Romains 1:20","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.22","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:22","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Se vantant d\u2019\u00eatre sages, ils sont devenus fous;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.23","name":"Romains 1:23","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.21","name":"Romains 1:21","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.23","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:23","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>et ils ont chang\u00e9 la gloire du Dieu incorruptible en images repr\u00e9sentant l\u2019homme corruptible, des oiseaux, des quadrup\u00e8des, et des reptiles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.24","name":"Romains 1:24","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.22","name":"Romains 1:22","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.24","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:24","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi Dieu les a livr\u00e9s \u00e0 l\u2019impuret\u00e9, selon les convoitises de leurs c\u0153urs; en sorte qu\u2019ils d\u00e9shonorent eux-m\u00eames leurs propres corps;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.25","name":"Romains 1:25","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.23","name":"Romains 1:23","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.25","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:25","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>eux qui ont chang\u00e9 la v\u00e9rit\u00e9 de Dieu en mensonge, et qui ont ador\u00e9 et servi la cr\u00e9ature au lieu du Cr\u00e9ateur, qui est b\u00e9ni \u00e9ternellement. Amen!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.26","name":"Romains 1:26","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.24","name":"Romains 1:24","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.26","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:26","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi Dieu les a livr\u00e9s \u00e0 des passions inf\u00e2mes: car leurs femmes ont chang\u00e9 l\u2019usage naturel en celui qui est contre nature;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.27","name":"Romains 1:27","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.25","name":"Romains 1:25","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.27","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:27","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>et de m\u00eame les hommes, abandonnant l\u2019usage naturel de la femme, se sont enflamm\u00e9s dans leurs d\u00e9sirs les uns pour les autres, commettant homme avec homme des choses inf\u00e2mes, et recevant en eux-m\u00eames le salaire que m\u00e9ritait leur \u00e9garement.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.28","name":"Romains 1:28","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.26","name":"Romains 1:26","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.28","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:28","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Comme ils ne se sont pas souci\u00e9s de conna\u00eetre Dieu, Dieu les a livr\u00e9s \u00e0 leur sens r\u00e9prouv\u00e9, pour commettre des choses indignes,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.29","name":"Romains 1:29","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.27","name":"Romains 1:27","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.29","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:29","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>\u00e9tant remplis de toute esp\u00e8ce d\u2019injustice, de m\u00e9chancet\u00e9, de cupidit\u00e9, de malice; pleins d\u2019envie, de meurtre, de querelle, de ruse, de malignit\u00e9;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.30","name":"Romains 1:30","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.28","name":"Romains 1:28","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.30","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:30","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>rapporteurs, m\u00e9disants, impies, arrogants, hautains, fanfarons, ing\u00e9nieux au mal, rebelles \u00e0 leurs parents, d\u00e9pourvus d\u2019intelligence,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.31","name":"Romains 1:31","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.29","name":"Romains 1:29","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.31","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:31","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.001.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>de loyaut\u00e9, d\u2019affection naturelle, de mis\u00e9ricorde.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.32","name":"Romains 1:32","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.30","name":"Romains 1:30","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.32","label":"","reference":"Romains 1:32","prev_osis_id":"Rom.001.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.002.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.1.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Et, bien qu\u2019ils connaissent le jugement de Dieu, d\u00e9clarant dignes de mort ceux qui commettent de telles choses, non seulement ils les font, mais ils approuvent ceux qui les font.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.1","name":"Romains 1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.2.1","name":"Romains 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.2.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.1.31","name":"Romains 1:31","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.1.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbeca85f3.65696524');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbeca85f3.65696524\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbeca85f3.65696524","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbeca85f3.65696524'); }","fums_noscript":